aints."}],"role":"sampleCode","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-406-swift-generics-expanded"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC18-223-Embracing-Algorithms":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-223-Embracing-Algorithms","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-223-embracing-algorithms","role":"sampleCode","abstract":[{"text":"When you imagine building a new app, what do you think about? Models, views, and controllers deserve their prominent place in the design process, but we don’t often give the same attention to the underlying work our apps need to do. Understand how to identify and optimize the algorithms in your app, and discover how implementing algorithms as generic protocol extensions results in efficient, effective, and maintainable code.","type":"text"}],"title":"Embracing Algorithms"},"zntfdr.jpeg":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg","type":"image"},"https://github.com/zntfdr":{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr","title":"GitHub","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"GitHub","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Contributions are welcome!","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","title":"Contributions are welcome!","type":"link"},"WWDC18-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC18-Icon.png","type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC19-215-Advances-in-Collection-View-Layout":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19-215-Advances-in-Collection-View-Layout","title":"Advances in Collection View Layout","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Collection View Layouts make it easy to build rich interactive collections. Learn how to make dynamic and responsive layouts that range in complexity from basic lists to an advanced, multi-dimensional browsing experience."}],"role":"sampleCode","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc19-215-advances-in-collection-view-layout"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC18":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","images":[{"identifier":"WWDC18-Icon.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"WWDC18.jpeg","type":"card"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18","role":"collectionGroup","title":"WWDC18","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 10, Swift 4.2, iOS 12, macOS 10.14 (Mojave), tvOS 12, watchOS 5."}]},"https://developer.apple.com/wwdc18/229":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc18\/229","type":"download","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc18\/229"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/zntfdr":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","images":[{"identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg","type":"card"},{"identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg","type":"icon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/zntfdr","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr","role":"sampleCode","title":"zntfdr (332 notes)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"No Bio on GitHub"}]},"https://":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Blog","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/","identifier":"https:\/\/","title":"Blog","type":"link"},"zntfdr":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/zntfdr.jpeg"}],"identifier":"zntfdr","alt":"Profile image of zntfdr","type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes"},"WWDC18.jpeg":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC18.jpeg","type":"image"}}}